      {
        "body": "We had an offline conversation on this.  We really appreciate you putting together this information.  We do think the information is useful as MSBuild can be an area that is daunting for people to start on but not everything in this document is accurate and we haven't had time to prioritize fixing that (and we can't approve an official document unless it's completely accurate).  One option we think may work here is moving community documents like this into the new GitHub discussions area: https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/discussions.  That wouldn't have the same high level bar we're holding for official documentation.  Thoughts?",
